\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 -Tabby's health and energy are increased periodically, by gaining levels, and after defeating bosses.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 -Tabby won't have any energy until she finds her first special ability that uses it.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
-The game starts on a space station built inside of an asteroid. This area contains mostly cargo and docking areas, hydroponics bays and workers quarters as well as power generators. Many areas of the station use the existing caverns to connect rooms. Thi
\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 s\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1  part of the game is fairly linear compared to when you take the space elevator down to the surface.
\par 
