\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Found: Starting weapon.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby's first weapon, it will likely be her main projectile weapon for some time. It has m\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
edium firing rate and does average damage to most living enemies, but does little damage to machines and ethereal enemies. However, it has umlimited ammunition.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Shotgun]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Found: On a dead crewman. 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby will find this weapon fairly soon after the power \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
has been turned on. High damage to anything live, but obviously with a low rate of fire. Average to little damage to machines, and ineffective against ethereals. Ammunition required.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Flamethrower]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Found: Undetermined
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Fires a steady steam of flame. A dev\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 astating weapon against living things, once set aflame they will quickly burn to their deaths. Ineffective against machines and ethereals. Ammunition required.

\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Lightning Gun]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Found: Undetermined
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
A fun weapon, it will automatically strike the closest enemy with a steady beam of electricity, shocking it to death. Shocked enemies, if not already dead when the beam is released, will have a recovery time before they can attack again. This weapon disab
\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 l\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 es most mechanical enemies,  but does average damage to ethereals. It drains its energy quickly, but gradually recharges on its own.it has a range of about a third of the screen.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Rocket Launcher]
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Found: Undetermined
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Self-explanatory weapon. :D
\par 
