\par 
\par }{\i\f1\fs20\insrsid11886834 \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Passive Abilities:}{\f1\fs20\insrsid11886834 \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1  These do not consume energy and are always active.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Double Jump]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 As the name states, Tabby can jump once more while in the air.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Regeneration]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby will slowly regenerate life over time.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Increased Energy Regeneration]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Increases how fast energy is recovered.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Enhanced Skin]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Reduces enemy damage, and allows Tabby to survive in harsh environments, including radioactive areas an\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 d the vaccuum of space.
\par 
\par }{\i\f1\fs20\insrsid11886834 \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Active abilties: }{\f1\fs20\insrsid11886834 
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Increased Speed]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Basically a speed booster.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Ethereal Form]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 While in this form, Tabby can not be hurt by physical attacks, and can pass through things such as grates. She is not completely invulnerable though\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
, as energy and non-physical attacks may still damage her. Reduces energy gradually.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Flight]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby can fly for a limited time with this ability. Drains energy quickly while in use. Maybe with pretty angel-wing particle effects :D
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Time control] 
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby can slow time down for her enemies.
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Teleportation]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Tabby can teleport a short distance. 
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Energy Pulse]
\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 Fires pulses of energy from her fingertips, consuming energy. It is the best weapon she has against ethereals so far. 
\par 
\par 
