\par 
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 [Critter] Small, but fast and annoying creature that normally keeps to itself unless it feels threatened, then it attacks quickly and fiercely. Easily killed, ho\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 wever.
